thread.title: Cleveland Mayor Frank Jackson to seek unprecedented fourth 4-year term
thread.title_full: Cleveland Mayor Frank Jackson to seek unprecedented fourth 4-year term

author: Leila Atassi, cleveland.com
title: Cleveland Mayor Frank Jackson to seek unprecedented fourth 4-year term
text: Cleveland Mayor Frank Jackson told friends and supporters Tuesday that he will run for an unprecedented fourth four-year term this November. Seven other candidates, so far, have pulled petitions to run against him.
